A multi-stage representation of cell proliferation as a
Markov process
Christian A. Yates1 Æ ,
1

Matthew J. Ford3,4 ,

Richard L. Mort2

Centre for Mathematical Biology, Department of Mathematical Sciences, University of Bath, Claverton
Down, Bath, BA2 7AY, UK.

2

Division of Biomedical and Life Sciences, Faculty of Health and Medicine, Furness Building, Lancaster
University, Bailrigg, Lancaster, LA1 4YG, UK.

3

MRC Human Genetics Unit, MRC IGMM, Western General Hospital, University of Edinburgh, Edinburgh, EH4 2XU, UK.

