Figure 3. Apc mutant daughters separate less frequently

858
859
860

(A) 3D projections of fixed organoids produced from small-intestinal crypts of wild-type and
ApcMin/+ mice stained with Hoechst (blue), phalloidin (red) and Îł-tubulin (green). ApcMin/+
